{"tid":112531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚漫]想搵一本漫畫....","createTime":"2017-02-08T08:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T09:50:43.000Z","uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c47e111529954e2de9cfa05fe3de3e65874f661a","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:09:35.000Z","msg":"好耐之前睇過，講幾十年後嘅日本好流行VR，毒撚男主角終於儲夠錢買一隻戀愛育成嘅VR game.。點知誤打誤撞買咗隻市面禁售嘅戀愛育成遊戲，因為入面嘅女角色會唔知點影響到真實世界....<br />\n<br />\n有一幕係講game入面可以同女主角啪啪啪，但係一定要另外買個vr飛機杯先可以令細佬有真實扑嘢嘅feel，男主角唔夠錢，唯有死求爛求佢個毒撚老死借個飛機杯俾佢做老襟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打睇過呢本嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7179155f3e7c1e6365c1810ce6e528279c9b576","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009f3248e82133d0f1f4ae4a20945c0016efbefe","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa703edd6498843ca1bb4d8fddb2f91bd22ef7b","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfddb116b201ac20bdfb966ae334bbf0d5c65a84","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e790b0e9e8df3d8492f58fb8509a6d838360dab6","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3501eb411ae800929fc0c3b19d3f2abdecdd5fa9","tid":112531,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2